    "MATERIALS AND METHODS A. MethodologyThis study employs a comprehensive mixed-methods approach to investigate the impact of chatbot applications on student achievement in Quantum Theory courses.",
    "The research aims to create tailored chatbot-supported activities for Quantum Theory and explore their integration across academic disciplines.",
    "The study adopts a robust quasi-experimental design, incorporating pre-test, post-test, and control groups, combined with qualitative and quantitative analyses [51].",
